"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-29-suspense-olympics-triathlon-seine-fails-water-tests\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Olympic organisers cancelled a second day of triathlon training in the River Seine on Monday due to water pollution, increasing uncertainty over whether the men's and women's races will go ahead as scheduled in the coming days.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"a second day\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 63}, {\"ngram\": \"triathlon training\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 114}, {\"ngram\": \"water pollution\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainty\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 161}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's and women's races\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming days\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's race is set to take place on Tuesday morning, with organisers set to make a last-minute decision when they have reviewed the latest laboratory results overnight.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men's race\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 286}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday morning\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"a last-minute decision\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest laboratory results\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The waterway is still polluted after heavy rain storms on Friday during the opening ceremony in Paris and again on Saturday, which led to discharges of raw sewage.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4137889505747579e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The waterway\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy rain storms\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"discharges\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"raw sewage\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a joint statement, Paris 2024 organisers and World Triathlon said they had taken the decision to cancel Monday's swimming training session because \\\"water quality levels\\u2026 do not present sufficient guarantees\\\" to allow it to take place.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.392269222321544e-24, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.805188688916634e-19, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a joint statement\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday's swimming training session\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality levels\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"sufficient guarantees\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They added, however, that they remained \\\"confident\\\" that pollution would drop before the start of competition given the current bright, sunny weather which helps keep bacteria levels down.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pollution\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the current bright, sunny weather\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria levels\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the men's triathlon does take place tomorrow it will be in high-temperatures above 30 degrees Celsius (86 degrees Fahrenheit), while a threat of storms has emerged that could have an impact on the women's race which is scheduled for Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's triathlon\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"high-temperatures\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"30 degrees\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"Celsius\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"storms\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"an impact\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's race\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christophe Calas, a weather forecaster based at the Paris 2024 organising committee, told reporters on Monday that storms were moving towards Paris from central France and could hit on Tuesday evening.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbp