 national forecaster Meteo France.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1588, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calas_(general)\", \"score\": 0.743301453656814, \"rank\": 0.28205128205123525, \"text\": \"Calas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calas_(general)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calas_(general)\"}, {\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9951036287405315, \"rank\": 0.004364639364506538, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"score\": 0.9999999998472049, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meteo France\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If there is a storm over Paris tomorrow night that results in significant amounts of precipitation that would have an impact on water quality in the Seine,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1681, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4137889505747579e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999572537, \"rank\": 3.9657022866777375e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra